;
; speech-loopback-capture-learning-band -- captured prompt improves toward oracle.
;
; Verdict 8191:
;   1    captured audio metadata is present
;   2    render amplitude is present
;   4    loopback envelope evidence is present
;   8    untrained model starts away from the observed feature
;   16   learned center reaches the observed feature
;   32   WER improves toward the oracle prompt
;   64   learned native WER reaches zero
;   128  clean learned sample carries native success
;   256  learned four-sample window routes native
;   512  receipt preserves loopback evidence
;   1024 receipt preserves nonzero audio hash
;   2048 clean sample carries no control debt
;   4096 receipt names the capture-learning row

(do
    (scl-on-device-check 16000 1 23200 23109 3006571 561
                         811960308 1491283 1045058 4 446225 129 9000 1))
